('ae34b532-c369-41a1-a37d-3c0cbd2d513f', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', '', '\nFrom now on, the Dresden Philharmonic offers tickets for refugees at the discounted price of 9.00 euros for all concerts (subject to availability). It is sufficient to show a identification document. Accompanying persons will also receive tickets for 9.00 Euro, for group sizes of 10 people the entrance for the accompanying person is free.', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', '5659870ce2899', 'en', '2015-11-28 14:04:28', '2016-06-21 17:23:02'),
