('ec3e28a4-8524-4b68-8e73-fab44d0af329', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', '', 'Youth Migration Service (German: Jugendmigrationsdienst / JMD)\n\nThe JMD is a counseling center for young migrants up to 27 years. It focuses on the consultation on matters of school, language, occupation and Studies Furthermore there is a specialist on child protection (§ 8a SGB VIII).', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', '556e1d54a8b19', 'en', '2015-06-02 23:17:53', '2016-06-21 17:23:01'),
